author: kaz
msg: Changed the formatting of the generated change log page.
- The log messages are now displayed with the most recent entries first
- The "Message" and "Files" columns have been merged into one column.
Previously, the width of the "Files" column was so large that the log
message column was very narrow resulting in an awkward presentation.
By merging the two columns together, the generated page is much easier
